title: World Air Routes - Varig 777
description:
After bringing you the B737-300, B737-700, B767-200, B767-300 and MD11, Varig returns to the World Air Routes series with the B777-200! 

 

You will sit in the cockpit for a Transatlantic flight from Sao Paulo to Madrid and back followed by a domestic flight from Sao Paulo to Manaus and back. See 4 takeoffs and 4 landings in the cockpit. Pilots will give you a variety of briefings and presentations about the flights and the aircraft. You'll go through the instruments, visit the equipment compartment located below the cockpit, the crew rest area behind the cockpit, learn about the procedures and much more
